          "text": "Buses replace trains between Secaucus Junction and Spring Valley",
          "language": "en-html"
        }]
      },
      "descriptionText": {
        "translation": [{
          "text": "All Pascack Valley Line trains are cancelled while NJ TRANSIT performs track work.\nExpress buses run between Spring Valley and Secaucus Junction, making intermediate stops at Nanuet and Pearl River. View the special timetable for bus departure times and stop locations.\nIf you are traveling to intermediate stops in New Jersey, local buses are also available.\nBetween Secaucus and Hoboken, use regular Main/Bergen County Line trains.\nIf possible, consider using the Hudson Line at Tarrytown station, which accepts Pascack Valley Line monthly and weekly tickets for travel to and from Manhattan.\n\nService resumes with the 12:45 AM from Hoboken to Spring Valley.",
          "language": "en"
        }, {
          "text": "\u003cp\u003eAll Pascack Valley Line trains are cancelled while NJ TRANSIT performs track work.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eExpress buses run between Spring Valley and Secaucus Junction, making intermediate stops at Nanuet and Pearl River. \u003ca title\u003d\"\" target\u003d\"_blank\" href\u003d\"https://d2g63oyneaimm8.cloudfront.net/sites/default/files/Bus%20schedule%20-%20PVL%20Busing%20-%20Saturday%201-29-22.pdf\" rel\u003d\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"\u003eView the special timetable\u003c/a\u003e for bus departure times and stop locations.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you are traveling to intermediate stops in New Jersey, local buses are also available.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eBetween Secaucus and Hoboken, use regular Main/Bergen County Line trains.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf possible, consider using the Hudson Line at \u003cstrong\u003eTarrytown \u003c/strong\u003estation, which accepts Pascack Valley Line monthly and weekly tickets for travel to and from Manhattan.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style\u003d\"min-height:10px\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eService resumes with the \u003cstrong\u003e12:45 AM\u003c/strong\u003e from Hoboken to Spring Valley.\u003c/p\u003e",
          "language": "en-html"
        }]
